    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ここは一体……",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "どうやら、さっきまでいた場所とは別の世界みたいね",
      "startTime": 3.3550794284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "きっと『ぴょんぴょんワープくんDXカスタム』に\nぶつかった時に、誤作動を起こして転送されたんだわ",
      "startTime": 11.3884127617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "でも変ね。エネルギーが足りなくて\nワープは出来なかったはずなのに……",
      "startTime": 18.721746095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたら元の場所に戻れるんですか？",
      "startTime": 21.3742407163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "私に分かる訳ないでしょ\nララならなんとか出来るかもしれないけど……",
      "startTime": 26.752743737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……ダメだわ\n電波が届いていないから、ララに連絡も出来ない",
      "startTime": 34.0860765617,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 32.552743737
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ここから脱出するには\n俺達で出口を探すしかないようですね",
      "startTime": 39.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、こんな訳の分からない場所に飛ばされて\nちゃんと帰れるのかしら",
      "startTime": 46.1434915226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "弱気になっちゃダメです。大丈夫、俺がついてますから\n一緒に出口を探しましょう",
      "startTime": 52.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nそうね。嘆いていても始まらないわ。行きましょう",
      "startTime": 57.1515643757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "うう……この地面、ぐにゃぐにゃして歩き辛いわね\n……きゃっ！",
      "startTime": 66.8848994892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですか！？　転ばないように俺に掴まって下さい\n遠慮しないで、しがみついていいですよ",
      "startTime": 72.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "しがみつくって……\nでも、今日の私は薄着だから、密着なんてしたら……",
      "startTime": 78.3148996037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、仕方ないわよね\nじゃあ、腕を借りるわ。離れないよう……強く……",
      "startTime": 87.3815713566,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3433.3320617999875,
          "startTime": 90.8149034184
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、ほら、もたもたしないで行くわよ\nさっさと歩きなさい！",
      "startTime": 97.3149046899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数十分後",
      "startTime": 99.7748398301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "結構歩いたのに、景色が全然変わらないわね\nまるで同じ所をぐるぐる歩き回っているみたいだわ",
      "startTime": 106.5482380232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "出口なんて影も形も見当たらない……\n私達は一生ここから出られないのかしら",
      "startTime": 114.3815703393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "弱音なんて莉央さんらしくないですよ\n大丈夫、必ず俺が莉央さんをみんなの所へ帰します",
      "startTime": 121.2066456951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう\n今日の貴方はめずらしく頼り甲斐があるわね",
      "startTime": 127.7851305645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "「めずらしく」って、そんなに普段は頼りないですか？\nこれでも精一杯やっているつもりなんですが",
      "startTime": 136.7999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……冗談よ。いつも頼りにしているわ。今だって\n貴方が一緒だから、私は落ち着いていられるのよ",
      "startTime": 146.168467204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがいてくれて良かったわ\n……これは私の本音よ",
      "startTime": 152.8351318361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんですか急に……\nあの莉央さんが素直に俺を褒めるなんて……",
      "startTime": 157.4000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "どうして意外そうな顔するのよ\n私が素直に感謝するのが、そんなにおかしいかしら",
      "startTime": 163.7814126016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、まぁ、私はララのように\n素直で可愛くはないけど……",
      "startTime": 172.1814197224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "え？\nなぜそこでララさんが出てくるんですか？",
      "startTime": 175.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "なぜって……さっき貴方が言ったんじゃない\nララみたいに素直で可愛い子が好きだって",
      "startTime": 182.2080871902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "spacetimegap-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あれは、ララさんがアイドルに向いているって\n話ですよ？",
      "startTime": 188.766675822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "素直で可愛いララさんがアイドルになれば\n沢山の人が好きになってくれると思うんです",
      "startTime": 193.3000091553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
